_source.name: Kapta Short 3.5"  Women's
_source.long_description: Running all day takes you farther along the trail and deeper into the wild around you. Your kit - footwear, hydration vest, clothing - needs to work as a system, freeing you to go far and fast. The Kapta Short combines advanced design, materials and patterning in a performance short for your longest runs. The light, breathable Teslin fabric is durable enough for mountain use and stretches for freedom on the move, and the generous 3/4 side slit and short 3.5 inch inseam allow for an easy stride.

_source.name: Camosun Parka Men's
_source.long_description: The Camosun is a modern, refined parka streamlined for urban environments. Stylish, warm and stormproof, the Camosun Parka delivers truly waterproof, windproof and breathable, weather protection on the harshest days. The Camosun uses an N150p-x GORE-TEX 2L face fabric that has a soft hand, supple feel and longwearing performance. Down Composite Mapping effectively places down and synthetic insulations where they deliver the most benefit. Lofty 750 fill power European Goose down lines the core and sleeves where loft is most needed. Because it retains warmth when wet, Coreloft synthetic insulation is used at the cuffs, hood and under the arms, areas prone to contact with moisture. Down Contour Construction allows the down to form to the body, enhancing thermal performance with a trimmer, more streamlined fit. The Coreloft insulated hood adds protection and warmth.
